name: WellingtonTrains
0:
”Alexa, ask wellington trains when the next train from Waterloo Station is”
”Alexa, ask wellington trains when the next train from Wellington Station is”
”Alexa, ask wellington trains when's the next train”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wellington trains
des:
This skill will tell you the time of the next train leaving from your requested station in Wellington, New Zealand.

Requesting Wellington Station will give you times for the next train on each of the lines that service the station.

Requesting any other station will give you the time of departure in each direction from that station.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
